Package: pping2
Version: 0.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Nikolay Shopik <shopik@nvcube.net>
Depends: libtins4.5, libpcap0.8t64, libstdc++6
Description: Passive TCP RTT measurement tool
 pping2 measures TCP round-trip time by passively monitoring active
 connections without injecting traffic. Includes SEQ/ACK measurement
 for flows without TCP timestamp option, aggregated output for
 ClickHouse ingest, and a systemd operational stack (service + timer).
